                  <img src="/images/iconos/instagram.png" alt="Instagram" style="margin: auto;">
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p class="rights wow fadeInUp"><span>&copy;&nbsp; </span><span class="copyright-year"></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span> BLUE HORIZON </span><span>.&nbsp;</span><span>All rights reserved.</span><br>David Galvez <br> Alejandro Lopez</p>
